org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers
Class AeBpelDefTraverserVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeAbstractDefVisitor
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.AeBpelDefTraverserVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeBPELConstants, IAeConstants, IAeDefVisitor
public class AeBpelDefTraverserVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefVisitor
implements IAeBPELConstants

Work horse class for traversing and serializing the AeProcessDef object model.
The traversal mechanism is driven an AeDefTraverser subclass, the AeInvokeWithScopeTraverser.

createElementAndTraverse

protected void createElementAndTraverse(AeBaseDef aDef,
                                        org.w3c.dom.Element aParentElementFromStack)
Creates an element for the def, adding it to the parent element passed in. The new element is then pushed onto the stack and we traverse the def to write all of its children. We then write any extensions for the def followed by a pop() and then done and done.

Parameters:
aDef -
aParentElementFromStack - will be null if writing the first node
